{"tid":662811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪一齊耐咗都會咁？","createTime":"2018-05-12T17:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T04:46:24.000Z","uid":170062,"like":12,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"608eef527965a2356e18702d6dc610daa3f7e9a6","tid":662811,"uid":170062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"初初一齊既時候 <br />\n如果我唔開心唔出聲<br />\n佢就會好緊張係咁問我咩事<br />\n我話需要空間靜下<br />\n佢都會一直搵我問我做咩<br />\n<br />\n而家一齊兩年幾<br />\n當我唔開心想靜下<br />\n佢就真係完全唔出現<br />\n連我熄咗電話都唔知⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實keep住熱情係咪真係好難？<br />\n定其實男人都係咁<br />\n一齊耐咗熱情就一定會減退？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果減退係一個定律<br />\n咁女人又應該做d咩<br />\n令到段關係更長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe2211b42f574496e3390f34c79a2af72f8f3a4","tid":662811,"uid":181065,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"一起耐咗，有問題不妨直接同對方講啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819e97f2fdac803fa65fb674a9dcca729ea8b1ac","tid":662811,"uid":31594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"608eef527965a2356e18702d6dc610daa3f7e9a6","tid":662811,"uid":170062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"初初一齊既時候 <br />\n如果我唔開心唔出聲<br />\n佢就會好緊張係咁問我咩事<br />\n我話需要空間靜下<br />\n佢都會一直搵我問我做咩<br />\n<br />\n而家一齊兩年幾<br />\n當我唔開心想靜下<br />\n佢就真係完全唔出現<br />\n連我熄咗電話都唔知⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實keep住熱情係咪真係好難？<br />\n定其實男人都係咁<br />\n一齊耐咗熱情就一定會減退？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果減退係一個定律<br />\n咁女人又應該做d咩<br />\n令到段關係更長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:51:49.000Z","msg":"有咩想講就直接同佢講<br />\n過黎人話你知其實你成日唔開心唔出聲 初時好緊張你 但一齊耐左次數多左 真係會攰 加上你自己都話要空間靜下 咁佢自己都休息下"},{"pid":"863e681b4bec5f52853643d7d6142ff0cef87e69","tid":662811,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"一齊左8年間完全無冷淡過，仲越黎越愛佢<br />\n反而係佢嫌棄返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a92b1914b6f07b0d2704b3e67d59c8da83d72c","tid":662811,"uid":151029,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"你自己話要靜吓嘅⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果想佢關心吓你就唔好口是心非啦絲打"},{"pid":"e54398fc6bb9dd967d1b11d6dee21574bb5924c7","tid":662811,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"其實我有同佢傾 <br />\n但傾完一個問題<br />\n好快又有另一個問題<br />\n而有d野 以前明明佢會做得好足<br />\n例如以前long d <br />\n佢會好願意講下對我既感受<br />\n但我番黎耐咗就會唔會再講<br />\n什至係話佢知我想佢講佢都唔會再做<br />\n<br />\n應該係我太執著以前既佢係點<br />\n而家既佢又變成點 <br />\n<br />\n絲打們究竟當你地發現男朋友唔同咗<br />\n你地會點樣過渡？ <br />\n<br />\n唉⋯我不斷調整自己個心態<br />\n調到連我自己都覺得好吃力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c7d591b402b83e6b79af3cdf5774669cf7ded3","tid":662811,"uid":170062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"863e681b4bec5f52853643d7d6142ff0cef87e69","tid":662811,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"一齊左8年間完全無冷淡過，仲越黎越愛佢<br />\n反而係佢嫌棄返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"巴打你既女朋友係點樣？ <br />\n性格同平時相處係如何？"},{"pid":"d6c432cb47c99e51044c71dfb78ebb229c2d2a57","tid":662811,"uid":88666,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:03:34.000Z","msg":"想點呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係你自己話想靜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img